text: King Koon, we will raise the Negro to prominence in sports and entertainment to make them appear as suitable mates for the white woman. This is a paraphrase of Israel Cohen's racial program to the 20th century, published in the early 1900s, which sets out a plan for the mongrelization of the white race through the intermixture of cons, through the glorification of the Negro as a celebrity figure. Thus, the lowly savage of darkest Africa has transposed into a King Koon figure and the gullible white population, especially the women, given their emotional mind, are conscripted into this mongrelization protocol, volunteering their daughters and selves as sacrificial gifts on the altar of egalitarian secular humanism, which has become established through the propaganda ministry as a new religion, any questioning of which becomes sin and sacrilege. The heresy of postmodernity, progress, it is called, this downward spiral trend of the subtle and gradual genocide and displacement of one's own kind with sub-IQ savages. The King Koon draped in golden jewels as a modern voodoo priest, a king Solomon, as put forth as a hero figure, a hypermasculine ubermenge, who constitutes the embodiment of virility thereby increasing the probability of his appeal to the na√Øve and brainwashed white masses. The males wanting to emulate this figure, the females to fornicate with him. Such is the intention of a Jewish mod manipulator who uses his system of illusion to create the reality of the desirability of what was only just a few decades ago looked upon as a lowly creature, only slightly elevated from the brute, and in fact debated as to whether he was not either the missing lake or an amalgam of beast and man, which ladders probably the reality from a bio-entropological standpoint. Portraying such a creature as the height of masculinity devolves masculinity and humanity to the level of a beast, which is the intention of the Jew to create their mongrelized and debased product of mixture, which would, so that they believe in their utopian fantasizing, control the entire world for themselves and enslave all others in their tyranny. The transposition of values here in consists of the negro, former brute, being elevated over the status of a white male, former inventor and creator, and the latter being demoted to the level of a wiggerized slave, useful only as a tool to be dispensed with once used up in its productive capacity. The end of its life force is a human battery to be done away with economically, replacement in occupation with non-whites and physically, through the alopathic genocide system. Thus, the white female, though instinctively gravitating toward their own kind as per natural inclinations, perversely shuns her own people through their having been stripped of their status as a valuable commodity and her economic worldview, libidinal economy and social economics. The prudential calculus of decision making on the basis of resource acquisition and provision, i.e. exploitation of man as a resource provider and status object. Given that the new normal socially engineered by the Jew is that the non-whites is giving everything under the Jew, of course, first among equals, the white male is looked upon as of subordinate status, and thus is cut out of the mating game thereby reducing the white birth rate and enabling the Jew to gain greater power and advantage as he hides behind his non-white fronts in the seats of power and claims of status of a humanitarian, a philanthropist who simply wants to give a non-whites a chance. A chance to rape and a chance to create Mongol offspring and to ruin the women of the white race who is naivety leads them to fall the way of all flesh. Whatever the Jew and his media portrays is socially acceptable, creating a new reality out of the old, reifying his ideals, the women being collectivists and replicating slash peridine, whatever the party line or more is of society happens to be at one moment or another, follow the crowd off the cliff and so long as they are not singled out as an outsider, eagerly go to their own destruction through the destruction of their family line. The white male has now been debased to the level of the brute, a worker, or a vagrant, an outcast who has no entitlement to be represented in his own ancestral territory. Of course, this will be construed as complaining to speak of the realities of life, but is an adequate representation of fact no mere opinion, and so far as the regime exists, this program of Mongolization will exist, and the process through which it is affected, the means to its realization will also exist. The solution is simply to detach oneself from the controlled system propaganda and to make a counter strike of anti-system propaganda, of rassan hygiene or racial purity in place of rassan and tartum or racial degeneration, to counter the Jews moves in the game of chess between darkness and light, and this through the propounding a traditionalist ethics and ideology which resurrects Allah-Lazurus, the stability of the kid culture and racial group, who only a few, if not only a single decade ago, was a much healthier world with people who actually had a consciousness which rejected the rot of rassan and tartum and understood its corrupting influence. However, what led us to the Demographic was a relentless demoralization protocol of the Jew which was used as a mechanism of eroding the healthy instincts of the white population. At this point there still exists the establishment of the Mongol as hero or anti-hero being in doubt with the supreme right to pontificate as a moral superior and to imply the immorality of the white population. However, the scales on the eyes of the broad masses are falling away and they no longer exalt to such an extent as they previously did the countable savage of darkest Africa as their primitive superman. No longer do the paintings of go-gen of brown tropical females or the bleeding and jarring cacophony of jazz music in a rap appeal to the sensibilities of the broad masses. For they are listening to the call of the blood memory which awakens in their consciousness and understanding of their traditions and identity enabling them to break free of the mold of the Zog Matrix and its anti-white protocols.
